This paper deals with natural language processing, machine learning, and data analysis to study the emotional trajectories of stories. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, it also involves supervised and unsupervised learning, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with data analysis and pattern recognition, which can be categorized under Cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper involves the digitization of text and the study of cultural evolution, which can be classified under Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
